OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUS to probe claims Sikh    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fturbans taken at border    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, US authorities say they are            
OL,6, investigating reports that the turbans 
OL,7, of Sikh asylum seekers were confiscated
OL,8, after they were detained at the border.
OL,10,FAccording to human rights advocates,   
OL,11,Fnearly 50 migrants have had religious  
OL,12,Fheadgear taken away.                   
OL,14,FSikhism requires that men wear turbans 
OL,15,Fand do not cut their hair.             
OL,17,FRecord numbers of migrants from India  
OL,18,Fhave been detained at the US-Mexico    
OL,19,Fborder in recent months.               
